query:
INSERT INTO portfolio_optimization_cache (
            portfolio_id,
            calculated_at,
            expires_at,
            recommendations,
            risk_free_rate,
            positions_analyzed,
            calculation_duration_ms
        )
        VALUES ($1, NOW(), $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
        ON CONFLICT (portfolio_id) DO UPDATE SET
            calculated_at = NOW(),
            expires_at = $2,
            recommendations = $3,
            risk_free_rate = $4,
            positions_analyzed = $5,
            calculation_duration_ms = $6
